title: Kyle Kinane, stand-up comedian - Episode 53
itunes:title: Kyle Kinane, stand-up comedian - Episode 53
description:
I was very excited to conduct this interview with Kyle Kinane, one of my favorite comedians around currently. We dive into his background of growing up in the Chicago punk scene, how the suburbs affect him and what a supportive family can end up doing to you.
